{"tid":1419413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地要將「五大訴求 缺一不可」依句口號宣揚開去","createTime":"2019-08-06T01:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T07:35:48.000Z","uid":61886,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03f0d9bea2b1b19cc5179c342bc07bf418857403","tid":1419413,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:15:00.000Z","msg":"我個人認為有以下好處<br />\n1. 做咩行動都好，唔會比人失焦既感覺，我地係追求緊五大訴求。<br />\n2. 避免左林奠換扣帽子。<br />\n3. 凝聚返淺黃或者偏中立既支持者。<br />\n<br />\n「光復香港」我地叫兩星期<br />\n已經差唔多係人都識叫<br />\n<br />\n我地唔使再分開叫五大訴求既口號<br />\n<br />\n直接<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「五大訴求，缺一不可」</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f87e52995dc7bf7e8ac0471c5308f000c9f8d8e5","tid":1419413,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:17:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2a6ba740ecdcc92c8e8086f7eb1d3201383f66","tid":1419413,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:20:39.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"7f7acb0d8d4fc085f188980b992d8fb4bfcc2ce2","tid":1419413,"uid":191656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f43af15e8821e3cad8905c1030f1b7b25a3101","tid":1419413,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:22:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3a7be6c392df012708b9164eedec99912571b1","tid":1419413,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b35e4a4adcacee57c167c3afe95e4bd35786fa7","tid":1419413,"uid":54149,"lik